# Build context = ./web (used by bff/Dockerfile). Keep host-built artefacts out of the
# image so the in-container `npm ci` / `nest build` are authoritative. In particular,
# a stale tsconfig.tsbuildinfo would make tsc's incremental build emit nothing after
# nest's deleteOutDir, leaving /app/bff/dist empty and breaking the runtime COPY.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.git
**/data
